videos.headline: Hosey Williams is relentless
videos.description: Cincinnati RB Hosey Williams is stuffed at the line of scrimmage, but keeps churning his legs and breaks free to score a 29-yard touchdown against Miami (FL).

videos.headline: Shaq Washington makes namesake proud with this punt return
videos.description: Cincinnati's Shaq Washington receives a punt on the far side of the field, then breaks into space for a 69-yard return for the Bearcats.

videos.headline: Hayden Moore continues to impress
videos.description: Cincinnati QB Hayden Moore extends the play, then finds Mekale McKay in the end zone for an 11-yard touchdown.
